#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The page also displays the first payment date for which the Schedule will be "
"created."
msgstr ""
"La page affiche aussi la date du premier remboursement programmé par cette "
"opération récurrente."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:668
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<screeninfo>Parent Account</screeninfo>"
